#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_freegrid
msgid "Architectural Excellence for Corporate Success"
msgstr "卓越建築，成就企業成功"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_cta_box
msgid "Book an appointment and see how we can unlock your potential<br/><br/>"
msgstr "預約商談，了解我們如何幫助你釋放最大潛力<br/><br/>"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_cta_box
msgid "Book now"
msgstr "立即預訂"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid "Detailed Project Management"
msgstr "精細專案管理"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Discover our latest collection: sustainable, innovative designs that blend "
"modern elegance with timeless architectural beauty."
msgstr ""
"探索我們的最新產品系列：可持續的創新設計，將現代優雅與永恆經典建築之美，融為"
"一體。"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_enark.field_theme_utils__display_name
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "顯示名稱"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Embrace eco-friendly architecture with sustainable design solutions that "
"reduce environmental impact."
msgstr "採用減低環境影響的可持續設計方案，擁抱環保建築。"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Experience seamless project execution with meticulous planning, budgeting, "
"and oversight from concept to completion."
msgstr ""
"體驗流暢無縫的專案執行：由構思至完工，都經過精心的策劃、財務預算及監督。"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_enark.field_theme_utils__id
msgid "ID"
msgstr "識別碼"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid "Innovative Design Solutions"
msgstr "創新設計方案"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_title
msgid "Innovative architecture <br/>and sustainable design solutions"
msgstr "創新建築及<br/>可持續設計方案"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_freegrid
msgid ""
"Our architectural solutions combine design excellence with business acumen, "
"creating spaces that inspire and support your corporate goals. Transform "
"your workspace with our expertise."
msgstr ""
"我們的建築解決方案，揉合卓越設計與商業頭腦，創造能夠激發創意、支援你企業目標"
"的辦公空間。利用我們的專業知識，讓你的工作空間蛻變。"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_freegrid
msgid "Start a Project"
msgstr "開展專案項目"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_cta_box
msgid "Still hesitating ?<br/>Contact us, it's free"
msgstr "還在猶豫？<br/>聯絡我們進行免費諮詢"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid "Sustainable Building Practices"
msgstr "可持續建築方式"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_enark.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "主題"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Transform your vision into reality with cutting-edge architectural designs "
"tailored to your unique needs and aesthetic preferences."
msgstr ""
"根據你的獨特需求及審美眼光，量身訂造最先進的建築設計，將你的願景變為現實。"
